    "description": "We at Siemens Healthineers India Advisory Limited are looking for an experienced Surgeon based out of Howrah. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Siemens Healthineers India Advisory Limited:\nSiemens Healthineers India Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in Medical Ethics\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Referral bonus program\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Howrah, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Siemens Healthineers India Advisory Limited!",
